{"root":{"data":{"id":"diuz3ep1gxc0","created":1780038806498,"text":"NLP+LLM"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuz3pux3og0","created":1780038830799,"text":"NLP","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-83.49999780952919,"y":-232.33332369393787},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuz4u1us740","created":1780038918289,"text":"01.自然语言处理","layout_right_offset":{"x":-6.6666662030749535,"y":-159.1666555984159},"priority":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuz8gy57bs0","created":1780039203223,"text":"NLP（Natural Language Processing⾃然语⾔处理）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.999999940395412,"y":-142.99999573826796},"priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzdutd5e80","created":1780039625230,"text":"文本分类","layout_right_offset":{"x":-15.999999523162955,"y":-104.99999687075626}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuze3okfdk0","created":1780039644531,"text":"序列标注","layout_right_offset":{"x":-7.999999761581307,"y":-100.99999698996544}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuze9wrexc0","created":1780039658087,"text":"⽂本⽣成","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.9999999403953552,"y":-99.99999701976799}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzeijettk0","created":1780039676871,"text":"问答系统","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999850988502,"y":-99.99999701976787}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzepzv4bc0","created":1780039693103,"text":"信息抽取","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.9999998807907104,"y":-109.99999672174454}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzf2vqc2o0","created":1780039721152,"text":"规则时代->统计时代->深度学习时代->大模型时代","layout_right_offset":{"x":-8.999999731779099,"y":-117.99999648332607}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuz8jfrnlc0","created":1780039208643,"text":"NLP中的文本量化—分词","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.9999999403953552,"y":-234.999989221494},"priority":2,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzipka9gg0","created":1780040005618,"text":"基于规则的分词","layout_right_offset":{"x":-10.999999672174681,"y":-29.99999910593033},"expandState":"expand","priority":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzjsg7lnc0","created":1780040090266,"text":"正向最⼤匹配算法+逆向最⼤匹配算法+双向最⼤匹配"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzkw42h5c0","created":1780040176603,"text":"缺点：OOV⽆解+歧义⽆法消解+⼈⼯维护成本⾼"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzld8rad40","created":1780040213892,"text":"基于统计的分词","priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzlp3kltc0","created":1780040239700,"text":"HMM分词 — 隐⻢尔可夫模型","layout_right_offset":{"x":-18.999999433755875,"y":-24.999999254942054}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzmnsxnj40","created":1780040315244,"text":"拉普拉斯平滑（Laplace Smoothing），也被形象地称为“加⼀平滑”。它是为了解决在统计概率时，\n\n由于样本数据不⾜⽽导致的“零概率”尴尬问题。 "},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzmzehcb40","created":1780040340492,"text":"Viterbi算法 — 逐步推导（核⼼重点）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-22.9999993145467,"y":-17.99999946355831}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzp1xx9dk0","created":1780040502749,"text":"Viterbi算法⽤动态规划求解最可能的状态序列，是HMM分词的核⼼。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzpn7bv1c0","created":1780040549030,"text":"⼦词分割（数据驱动，⼦词级）","priority":3},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzrkb2mds0","created":1780040699455,"text":"BPE算法（Byte Pair Encoding）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-0.9999999701976776,"y":-11.999999642372131}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzu31z1wg0","created":1780040896992,"text":"不断找出文本中出现频率最高的“相邻字符对”，把它们合并成一个“新词（Subword）”，直到达到预设的词表大小。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzua4o65k0","created":1780040912392,"text":"WordPiece算法","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.999999850988388,"y":-6.999999791383743}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzwkb1oe00","created":1780041091274,"text":"它的核心思想是：我们要合并那些“一旦出现，就大概率是粘在一起”的组合，而不是仅仅因为它们各自都很常见才凑巧碰在一起。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzx167tvs0","created":1780041127987,"text":"Unigram算法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzz0gahgg0","created":1780041283148,"text":"Unigram 是自顶向下、基于概率剪枝的子词分词算法，通过保留重要子串、剔除冗余，得到紧凑且概率最优的词表，擅长多切分与无分隔符语言。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzz840aa00","created":1780041299819,"text":"SentencePiece：语⾔⽆关的分词⼯具"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0027dhy00","created":1780041365326,"text":"主流分词⼯具简介"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div007g5t1c0","created":1780041376742,"text":"jieba分词（第⼀代+第⼆代）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div00bedmyo0","created":1780041385341,"text":" HuggingFace tokenizers（第三代"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div00ut6uq00","created":1780041427595,"text":"分词工具","layout_right_offset":{"x":-6.2499997206032845,"y":-173.74999223276996}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div01cr4hgg0","created":1780041466652,"text":"jieba特点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div01e94coo0","created":1780041469917,"text":"cut(text) \n最精确，适合⽂本分析","layout_right_offset":{"x":-10.999999672174454,"y":-65.99999803304678}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div01rl4nm80","created":1780041498942,"text":"cut(text, cut_all=True)把句⼦中所有的可以成词的词语都扫描出来, 速度⾮常快，但是不能解决歧义"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}